    <item>
      <title>你说得对！但是优乐美奶茶可不会讲道理！</title>
      <link>https://juiceright.github.io/posts/2026/%E4%BD%A0%E8%AF%B4%E5%BE%97%E5%AF%B9%E4%BD%86%E6%98%AF%E4%BC%98%E4%B9%90%E7%BE%8E%E5%A5%B6%E8%8C%B6%E5%8F%AF%E4%B8%8D%E4%BC%9A%E8%AE%B2%E9%81%93%E7%90%86/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 16 Jan 2026 22:38:02 +0000</pubDate><author>cuiyu388@gmail.com (Juiceright)</author>
      <guid>https://juiceright.github.io/posts/2026/%E4%BD%A0%E8%AF%B4%E5%BE%97%E5%AF%B9%E4%BD%86%E6%98%AF%E4%BC%98%E4%B9%90%E7%BE%8E%E5%A5%B6%E8%8C%B6%E5%8F%AF%E4%B8%8D%E4%BC%9A%E8%AE%B2%E9%81%93%E7%90%86/</guid>
      <description>&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;99元4杯的优乐美能有什么坏心思呢的&#34;&gt;9.9元4杯的优乐美能有什么坏心思呢的😋&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;s&gt;如果能变成一杯优乐美，被女孩喜欢该多好（不是炫压抑）&lt;/s&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; src=&#34;https://juiceright.github.io/images/202601/%E4%BD%A0%E8%AF%B4%E5%BE%97%E5%AF%B9%EF%BC%81%E4%BD%86%E6%98%AF%E4%BC%98%E4%B9%90%E7%BE%8E%E5%A5%B6%E8%8C%B6%E5%8F%AF%E4%B8%8D%E4%BC%9A%E8%AE%B2%E9%81%93%E7%90%86%EF%BC%81/%E4%BD%A0%E8%AF%B4%E5%BE%97%E5%AF%B9%EF%BC%81%E4%BD%86%E6%98%AF%E4%BC%98%E4%B9%90%E7%BE%8E%E5%A5%B6%E8%8C%B6%E5%8F%AF%E4%B8%8D%E4%BC%9A%E8%AE%B2%E9%81%93%E7%90%86%EF%BC%81-20260116224426570.jpg&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;只是小小流感罢了&#34;&gt;只是小小流感罢了💪&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; src=&#34;https://juiceright.github.io/images/202601/%E4%BD%A0%E8%AF%B4%E5%BE%97%E5%AF%B9%EF%BC%81%E4%BD%86%E6%98%AF%E4%BC%98%E4%B9%90%E7%BE%8E%E5%A5%B6%E8%8C%B6%E5%8F%AF%E4%B8%8D%E4%BC%9A%E8%AE%B2%E9%81%93%E7%90%86%EF%BC%81/%E4%BD%A0%E8%AF%B4%E5%BE%97%E5%AF%B9%EF%BC%81%E4%BD%86%E6%98%AF%E4%BC%98%E4%B9%90%E7%BE%8E%E5%A5%B6%E8%8C%B6%E5%8F%AF%E4%B8%8D%E4%BC%9A%E8%AE%B2%E9%81%93%E7%90%86%EF%BC%81-20260116224426578.jpg&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;饮料家族合影&#34;&gt;饮料家族合影&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;每次刚考完试都会去零食有鸣整点吃的 &lt;s&gt;，但每次都只带回一些饮料之类的🥤&lt;/s&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; src=&#34;https://juiceright.github.io/images/202601/%E4%BD%A0%E8%AF%B4%E5%BE%97%E5%AF%B9%EF%BC%81%E4%BD%86%E6%98%AF%E4%BC%98%E4%B9%90%E7%BE%8E%E5%A5%B6%E8%8C%B6%E5%8F%AF%E4%B8%8D%E4%BC%9A%E8%AE%B2%E9%81%93%E7%90%86%EF%BC%81/%E4%BD%A0%E8%AF%B4%E5%BE%97%E5%AF%B9%EF%BC%81%E4%BD%86%E6%98%AF%E4%BC%98%E4%B9%90%E7%BE%8E%E5%A5%B6%E8%8C%B6%E5%8F%AF%E4%B8%8D%E4%BC%9A%E8%AE%B2%E9%81%93%E7%90%86%EF%BC%81-20260116224426580.jpg&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;不是因为寂寞才想你&#34;&gt;不是因为寂寞才想你&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; src=&#34;https://juiceright.github.io/images/202601/%E4%BD%A0%E8%AF%B4%E5%BE%97%E5%AF%B9%EF%BC%81%E4%BD%86%E6%98%AF%E4%BC%98%E4%B9%90%E7%BE%8E%E5%A5%B6%E8%8C%B6%E5%8F%AF%E4%B8%8D%E4%BC%9A%E8%AE%B2%E9%81%93%E7%90%86%EF%BC%81/%E4%BD%A0%E8%AF%B4%E5%BE%97%E5%AF%B9%EF%BC%81%E4%BD%86%E6%98%AF%E4%BC%98%E4%B9%90%E7%BE%8E%E5%A5%B6%E8%8C%B6%E5%8F%AF%E4%B8%8D%E4%BC%9A%E8%AE%B2%E9%81%93%E7%90%86%EF%BC%81-20260116230836433.jpg&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;h5 id=&#34;高清壁纸存个档&#34;&gt;&lt;s&gt;高清壁纸存个档&lt;/s&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; src=&#34;https://juiceright.github.io/images/202601/%E4%BD%A0%E8%AF%B4%E5%BE%97%E5%AF%B9%EF%BC%81%E4%BD%86%E6%98%AF%E4%BC%98%E4%B9%90%E7%BE%8E%E5%A5%B6%E8%8C%B6%E5%8F%AF%E4%B8%8D%E4%BC%9A%E8%AE%B2%E9%81%93%E7%90%86%EF%BC%81/%E4%BD%A0%E8%AF%B4%E5%BE%97%E5%AF%B9%EF%BC%81%E4%BD%86%E6%98%AF%E4%BC%98%E4%B9%90%E7%BE%8E%E5%A5%B6%E8%8C%B6%E5%8F%AF%E4%B8%8D%E4%BC%9A%E8%AE%B2%E9%81%93%E7%90%86%EF%BC%81-20260116230907394.png&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;</description>
